Method B: sub-step resource integration at FIXED (g, delta, L). n=1 is the orig model.
If alpha* converges as n grows, the residual IS resource-discretization and we can
read off the discretization-free alpha* at each cell.

P=1.0 L=40 (g=delta=0.02500)
 nsub   alpha*  decrement
    1    1.950           
    2    1.950     +0.000
    4    1.950     +0.000
    8    1.950     +0.000
   16    1.950     +0.000
   32    1.950     +0.000

P=1.0 L=80 (g=delta=0.01250)
